    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apple 是一款点击游戏，您可以点击 A̵͉͇̞͋̉p̶̻̝̠͍͗̍͜p̴̺̲̅̌͑͝l̶̛̠̱̾̋̒e̸̥͖̓̇͆̇̅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中花时间获得一个随机苹果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This weeks leaderboard:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1- foGokSa</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2- kitt</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3- 烏兎</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4- Arda Diller</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5- Senshi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6- jaQueem</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7- Arthur</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8- Hummass</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9- Korean Jesus</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10- cafeziinhuu </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以下是功能：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >苹果可以扩充您的收藏<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066470/extras/eff41ceb53889f8a597de0a51117f929.avif?t=1768816051\" width=256 height=256 /></span>收集神秘的苹果！（天知道是什么……）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >苹果箱<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066470/extras/700c172102a4e9981c44c46ebcab36dc.avif?t=1768816051\" width=512 height=512 /></span>购买、获得和打开创造物以获得惊喜！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 一些好消息<br>点击时阅读有趣而有趣的新闻！其中一些：<br>- 新闻快讯：禁果实际上是香蕉。苹果的公关团队正在加班加点。<br>- 一天一个苹果，医生远离你……如果你瞄准目标的话。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成就<br>通过点击并在游戏中获得高分来获得成就！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >排行榜<br>勇敢获得最高分的人将在 Discord 中获得奖励，他们的名字将在游戏中显示！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拥有特殊苹果和角色的社区<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066470/extras/a3740f7c3d7b841cdc71f15981ddfd07.avif?t=1768816051\" width=658 height=512 /></span>来 discord 加入我们的社区吧！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 Discord 提交设计！没错！您可以创建自己的苹果并将其添加到游戏中，快来加入我们的乐趣吧！</p>",
